01:33:45.499 --> 01:33:48.175
But I go to bring Nirmala.

01:33:48.376 --> 01:33:50.229
I go to bring her here?

01:33:50.430 --> 01:33:53.567
Not necessary, it’s all right.

01:34:05.840 --> 01:34:08.326
